Koi Fish keyboard theme will make your device look amazing! Download the Koi Fish skin with Koi Fish effect. Koi Fish only works with TouchPal keyboard installed on your phone!
Koi Fish is a fantastic keyboard theme with Koi Fish background. This beautiful keyboard is designed for people who like Koi Fish. Free download and apply this keyboard theme called Koi Fish, and Android stylized. Koi Fish is designed to give you a faster and smoother mobile keyboard experience. Also you can now express your emotions via messaging apps using the middle finger emoji, taco emoji, hot dog emoji, 100 sign emoji and can even send a unicorn face by this keyboard!!! Download this Koi Fish keyboard theme and type faster than ever. 
Your keyboard looks totally luxury with Koi Fish. Download Koi Fish theme and Try it out! Koi Fish will let a plain keyboard into a beautiful and unique one. Koi Fish can be used for different IM applications such as Instagram, Messenger, BeeTalk, Facebook Lite, ES File Explorer File Manager, Facebook Lite and so on, which mean Koi Fish can help you get more quickly in these apps.
How do I apply for Koi Fish keyboard theme?
Note: You need to download TouchPal keyboard first.
1) Download Koi Fish and click the INSTALL button.
2) Download "TouchPal Keyboard" from the Google Play Store. If you have already installed "TouchPal keyboard", please click the "APPLY" button.
3) "keyboard" installed and applied, Koi Fish will automatically install on the phone.
